22. Final product call

Backfill Shifts should be built as:

a lightweight, text-first scheduling and coverage operating mode that can stand on its own, while still supporting integrations for customers who want them.

Do not clone Microsoft Shifts as a product.
Do borrow:

import ergonomics
publish/share mental model
copy/reuse pattern

Do not inherit:

full Teams-style collaboration complexity
time tracking scope
enterprise-heavy settings surface

That is the right strategic line.
